                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7029" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1097</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7981 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">频频踩雷外债，阳光100还能否重见阳光？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Foreign debt defaults frequently, can Sunshine 100 turn the crisis around?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何帆，吴熙，王子怡，王瑞玥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">阳光100中国控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外债违约；阳光100；房地产行业；风险管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">External Debt Default; Sunshine 100; Real Estate Industry; Risk Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着融资新规的实施，我国房地产行业宏观调控加强、房地产开发企业的境内融资渠道全面收紧，许多房企转向量化宽松政策下处于利率低位的国际资本市场进行境外筹资。然而，我国房企盲目大量发行外债、忽视风险管理致使近年来我国外债违约事件接连发生，其中，民营房企问题尤为突出。本案例以阳光100中国控股有限公司（以下简称“阳光100”）为例，对阳光100从行业的后起之秀到负债累累，从积极转型到两度外债违约的公司发展历程、经营状况以及外债违约事件始末进行回顾，分析阳光100接连发生外债违约的深层原因和不利影响。试图通过对阳光100两度外债违约的分析，引导学生深入思考我国房地产民营企业应当如何应对今后经营过程中可能出现的现金流困境。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the implementation of the new financing regulations, the macro-control of China&#39;s real estate industry has been strengthened, the domestic financing channels of real estate development enterprises have been comprehensively tightened, and many housing enterprises have turned to the international capital market with low interest rates under the quantitative easing policy for overseas financing. However, China&#39;s housing enterprises blindly issued a large number of foreign debt and neglected risk management, resulting in a series of default events in China&#39;s foreign debt in recent years, of which the problem of private housing enterprises is particularly prominent. In this case, taking Sunshine 100 China as an example, sunshine 100 reviews the development history, operating conditions and foreign debt default events of Sunshine 100 from a rising star in the industry to a debt-ridden company, from active transformation to two foreign debt defaults, and analyzes the deep causes and adverse effects of Sunshine 100&#39;s successive foreign debt defaults. This paper attempts to guide students to think deeply about how private real estate enterprises in China should deal with the cash flow dilemma that may arise in the future business process through the analysis of the two foreign debt defaults of Sunshine 100.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">优序融资理论；等级筹资理论；债务危机的概念；违约债券的主要处置方；债券违约的影响</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
